00:23:20.348 --> 00:23:22.407
Sorry, UV radiation.

00:23:22.407 --> 00:23:23.778
Diana: Radiation.

00:23:23.778 --> 00:23:31.597
Ellen: Yeah, so yeah, with a UV, do you call

00:23:31.597 --> 00:23:33.178
it a radiator then?

00:23:33.178 --> 00:23:34.178
It's radiation.

00:23:34.178 --> 00:23:38.008
The UV torch, you can see, like, things that
you can't see a normal light.

00:23:38.008 --> 00:23:45.098
Like I said, like past retouching or a varnish
that's been applied is transparent in regular

00:23:45.098 --> 00:23:46.098
light.

00:23:46.098 --> 00:23:49.298
And I really…I love this style flashlight
