00:24:02.658 --> 00:24:06.927
Diana: Yeah, this a good shape for us.

00:24:06.927 --> 00:24:09.178
Ellen: What other tools do we have here?

00:24:09.178 --> 00:24:10.178
Diana: Let's see.

