So people ask us about tools a lot so we thought
we'd show you a couple of our favorite tools.

00:24:25.178 --> 00:24:29.467
For example, a dental pick.

00:24:29.467 --> 00:24:32.038
We borrow a lot from other professions.

00:24:32.038 --> 00:24:40.607
There's very few things…there's a few things,
