00:25:32.107 --> 00:25:33.107
Diana: Burnishing.

00:25:33.107 --> 00:25:34.107
Ellen: Burnishing.

00:25:34.107 --> 00:25:35.678
Diana: Different types of paint, you know,

00:25:35.678 --> 00:25:36.678
building.

00:25:36.678 --> 00:25:38.197
Ellen: Yeah, you sort of make paint look almost

