00:27:19.788 --> 00:27:27.957
It was just the right strength and thinness
to get the gunk off without damaging the surface.

00:27:27.957 --> 00:27:29.828
So yeah, this is one of my favorite tools.

00:27:29.828 --> 00:27:31.747
Diana: You could probably also cut it into

00:27:31.747 --> 00:27:37.098
weird shapes and then I'd stick it on to a
