00:28:13.518 --> 00:28:14.518
Ellen: Rayleigh scattering.

00:28:14.518 --> 00:28:16.508
Diana: Rayleigh scattering, so you want…it's

00:28:16.508 --> 00:28:21.597
nice to use a gray palette and yeah, so this
